             was indicted for <rs id="t17730626-4-off13" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17730626-4-off13" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17730626-4-off13" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a bank note, value 40 l. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17730626-4-victim73" type="victimName">
                           John
                            Crofts
                        <interp inst="t17730626-4-victim73" type="surname" value="Crofts"></interp>
